+ * @file
+ * Shared parser for the vmaf-tune qpfile format. Consumed by libx264,
+ * libsvtav1, and libaom-av1 encoder adapters via the new -qpfile
+ * AVOption.
+ *
+ * Patches 0007-0009 of ffmpeg-patches/ must keep this parser shared
